The genus Abaxisotima Gorochov (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Phaneropterinae) from ChinaTwo new species, Abaxisotima macrocaudata sp. nov. and Abaxisotima forcipiforma sp. nov., are described and illustrated, supplemental illustrations of several known species are provided. A key to species of the genus Abaxisotima Gorochov is presented. The type specimens are deposited in the Museum of Hebei University.